SUMMARY:August 2026 General Meeting: HHA Night at the Theatre
DTSTAMP:20260627T134348Z
DTSTART:20260810T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Houston Heights Association General Meeting on 
	Wednesday\, August 11 at 7:30 PM for a special community night out: HHA Ni
	ght at the Theatre! \nWe are heading to the Alley Theatre for a thrilling 
	performance of The Girl on the Train. Come early to mix\, mingle\, and sip
	 a drink with your neighbors before the show begins. \nTicket Information:
	 To join our neighborhood block\, visit www.alleytheatre.org/the-girl-on-t
	he-train. Be sure to enter the coupon code HHA before choosing your perfor
	mance date to access our special community arrangement. \nEvent Details: \
	n\n\nDate: Wednesday\, August 11\, 2026 \n\n\nTime: 7:30 PM \n\n\nVenue: A
	lley Theatre \n\n\nWebsite: www.alleytheatre.org/the-girl-on-the-train\n\n
	https://houstonheights.org/event/august-2026-general-meeting/\n\nFrom Hous
	ton Heights Association
